Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.65,0:00:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是奇怪的乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件超越想象中的發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清事實的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.10,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機 等等 還有人要上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.76,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你這個要買那個也要買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己還不是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了正在降價的進口貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我很早就想要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到站的時候記得叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘老人失蹤事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於中招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.11,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這個直接撞到了肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你不是毛利的女兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問伯伯是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做設樂 設樂重吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能怪你不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設樂先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個名字真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做毛利蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真悶熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因爲是下雨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.36,0:04:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝你 還寫出來給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實其我正想要去找你父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找他有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.14,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲用電話是說不清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫院還沒到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.83,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室町醫院嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有4站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到的時候我再告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的要謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.39,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麽時候啊 快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要到傢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 是我拜託你叫醒我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在變成我在叫你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 室町醫院前那個站呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就過站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個伯伯下車了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.46,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個老伯伯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像叫做設樂先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就坐在我的旁邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麽知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有看到那個老伯伯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因爲園子剛才在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就不要問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是在做夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問在室町醫院前那個站有個老伯伯下車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著一頂帽子拿著一把傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏上下車的人很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣 要不要去吃點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.16,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 你陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎麽辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.23,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽那麽在意那個老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那個老伯伯好像在哪見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.12,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總想不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.44,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我正想要去找你父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯好像有事要找我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣應該去那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花新聞社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設樂重吉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 在來慰問的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有住院的病人裏面都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老伯伯說要去醫院的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是來探病的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來探病的客人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有叫做設樂這個名字的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你擔心過度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有事要找你爸爸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會打電話到事務所去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是從一開始就沒有那個老伯伯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你還是不相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子說大概是我在做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總覺得好像不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如叫目暮警官幫忙找老伯伯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是想多了在做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許真的是我在做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MO磁碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.79,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麽啊 我不記得有買過這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是那位老伯伯的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有密碼就不能打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極秘 嚴禁帶出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會要密碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.30,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 可不可以解開密碼看看裏面是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要花一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.15,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不急著要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.21,0:09:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在去中午搭的那個巴士的公司看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還有別的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.90,0:09:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 等我確認過檔案之後再通知你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.59,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.20,0:09:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 是嗎 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 剛才問過巴士公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛巴士還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.81,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽我也要一起去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南說與其我一個人不如園子陪我一起找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也許可以記起些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 幫幫忙吧 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我剛剛沖完涼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 不要這樣 很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 那輛車…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.25,0:10:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒車子啊 快坐好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和中午那時候講的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不記得有什麽老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.03,0:11:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.66,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許老伯伯坐過的位置可能會留下什麽線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.09,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不是這輛巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛巴士有點問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在工廠裏維修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是指你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.78,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人問過我 那個叫毛利的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏下車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什麽意思 嚇死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麽樣的人問的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽樣的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他穿著外套戴著墨鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走吧 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的MO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴墨鏡的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麽問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在這裏等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 這麽可以隨便上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 有東西忘記拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.25,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裏 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.15,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在這裏 老伯伯就在旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得些什麽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.30,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 寫了名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候因爲玻璃有霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以用手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的不是在做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.73,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事 我完全搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.51,0:13:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開密碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 關於磁片裏面的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.73,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雙重帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道米花建設吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從那個公司的經理部拿出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是對外公開帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個是內部的帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面連政治傢對一些企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.38,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後交易的名單都排列出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老伯伯因爲有雙重帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會找我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那個戴墨鏡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標不是我 而是老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲發覺有人在跟蹤他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把MO磁碟放到小蘭姐姐你的包裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.92,0:14:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 他也知道我是毛利小五郎的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快找到老伯伯才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯自從下車之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是把雙重帳簿交給我後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到新聞社去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們仔細想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴墨鏡的人問了司機關於小蘭姐姐的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.63,0:15:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 他知道老伯伯身上並沒有帳簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.20,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會找坐在老伯伯旁邊的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯在戴墨鏡的人的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 你去通知叔叔和警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.31,0:15:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去老伯伯下車的地方看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲小蘭姐姐被人盯著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還是留在巴士公司比較安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 借個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.04,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.10,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 爸爸你有沒有在聽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽 我在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在這麽緊急的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣 馬上過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全醉了 我打電話給目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外型還不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我現在在平安巴士公司裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個女孩被抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才接到蘭的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說園子被抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.03,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的車子好像從巴士公司門口往左邊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊就是…這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機伯伯 請調頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.44,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽這麽慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因爲找不到機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.56,0:17:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該是和犯人的車子碰頭的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個方嚮只有一間工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說 一定是在某處轉彎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機伯伯 前面右轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路通到哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不通哪裏 這是通往倉庫的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要去別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須繞遠路才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.33,0:18:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說園子就在這附近的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是米花建設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.33,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 如果雙重帳簿被公開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到影響的不只是米花建設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和牠有內部交易的公司都有影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 在MO裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有一個龍神經濟研究所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且金額非常的大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不是這個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是另外一個女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.78,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然抓錯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲她背著皮包 所以我以爲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次 把她抓回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可別失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些人怎麽處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們身上沒有磁片就沒有用處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們處理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南 是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跑來這裏胡鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來戴墨鏡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是和米花建設有內部交易的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聘請的黑道人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而設樂重吉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米花建設的老員工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在不知如何是好之時將雙重帳簿帶了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖好你沒事 太好了園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花建設收到一封廉政公署的控告信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.80,0:21:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個有勇氣的老員工的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.25,0:22:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.93,0:23:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得在哪見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還想不起來嗎 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.21,0:23:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.71,0:23:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老伯伯是米花建設的老員工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.54,0:23:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許上過電視或者報紙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.11,0:23:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.92,0:23:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 二樓的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三明治和冰咖啡 還有橙汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.78,0:23:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.89,0:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是在做夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.10,0:23:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不是在做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.33,0:23:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.68,0:23:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來 設樂先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛利偵探事務所樓下咖啡廳的常客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.19,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子上面被裝了炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.99,0:24:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.75,0:24:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個人..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.88,0:24:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不覺得很像那個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.37,0:24:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要去小惠小姐傢的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.33,0:24:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途在狹窄的路上開快車的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.63,0:24:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.25,0:24:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車爆炸事件的真相(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.54,0:24:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.89,0:24:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒車入庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.75,0:24:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是事後恍然大悟的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開所有雜誌還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.38,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.74,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有適合我的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.89,0:00:33.80,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都無法討得你的歡心 惹得你滿腔怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.64,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉如臨深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.48,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.61,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.60,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.00,0:00:59.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.22,0:01:08.32,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到緊要關頭不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.12,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要用冷淡的眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.94,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用自己的速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.31,0:01:20.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我馬上會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.14,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.68,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.31,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.98,0:21:32.66,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這孕育著神秘的夜裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.16,0:21:37.30,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉上眼睛 獻上你的祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.08,0:21:43.64,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這月光融融的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.25,0:21:50.06,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我們因爲愛而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.33,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.94,0:22:07.56,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看未來化爲碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.86,0:22:16.34,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 赤著腳 踩在大地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:21.76,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.54,0:22:28.28,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱 抓住胸前的十字架 在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.42,0:22:34.60,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望照燿著你 在夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.72,0:22:40.78,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的光芒 將你擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.93,0:22:47.50,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠爲你停留 爲你的愛而停留
